title: Episode 53 Ft Valerie Lora
itunes:title: Episode 53 Ft Valerie Lora
description:
Valerie Lora sits in the hot seat with Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire and Stephanie Santiago and they discuss their get ready for summer tips, colonics, making new friends with guys who are attracted to you, and whether or not you can meet a quality man in the club.
